        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="UU6tTepPwgvEvhT8yv_2-16" value="&amp;nbsp;bind mount&amp;nbsp;" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;fontSize=12;startSize=8;endSize=8;" parent="1" source="UU6tTepPwgvEvhT8yv_2-15" target="UU6tTepPwgvEvhT8yv_2-13" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-0.2522" y="2" relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint as="offset" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="UU6tTepPwgvEvhT8yv_2-17" value="&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Un contenidor és un procés aïllat dins d&#39;un sistema host (kernel + distribució Linux). &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;En aquest cas, el host és un Linux Alpine que s&#39;executa dins d&#39;una màquina virtual lleugera (WSL2) gestionada per Windows. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;El contenidor inclou la seva pròpia distribució Linux, però comparteix el kernel amb el host.  Diversos contenidors poden tenir distribucions Linux diferents, però tots comparteixen el mateix kernel del host.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Des del contenidor es pot accedir a: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Windows&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Sistema de fitxers — via bind mount (el directori del projecte, per exemple)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Linux Host (Alpine/WSL2)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Dispositius del kernel —&amp;nbsp;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;/dev/ttyUSBx&lt;/code&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;/dev/bus/usb&lt;/code&gt;, etc.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Sockets Unix.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Xarxa&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bridge (per defecte)&lt;/strong&gt; — el contenidor té la seva pròpia IP virtual i accedeix a l&#39;exterior via NAT a través del host.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Host&lt;/strong&gt; — el contenidor comparteix directament la interfície de xarxa del host, sense NAT ni IP pròpia.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-2375" y="-1016" width="621" height="474" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="I-GqzyZJSIOx9jBOWlrk-1" value="diagrama_capes_docker.drawio" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-2084" y="-1062" width="60" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
